---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
import Topic from "./Topic.astro"
---
<Container>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row" id="projects">
    <Topic
      title="Case Studies"
      description="Explore Real-Life Examples of Our Proven Digital Marketing & AI Success"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full p-12 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- NEW: Secure Tax Platform -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 px-2 md:px-6 py-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/0">
        <p class="text-lg font-normal">
          For a tax services company, we built a highly secure, role-based platform where clients,
          tax specialists, and admins collaborate in real time. It includes encrypted document
          exchange, e-signature, granular permissions, and audit logs—streamlining filings while
          maintaining rigorous compliance.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/case-studies/tax-platform" class="text-[#93C5FD] text-xl leading-7">Learn more</a>
          <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- NEW: Hotel & Resort Chatbots -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 px-2 md:px-6 py-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/0">
        <p class="text-lg font-normal">
          For multiple hotels and resorts, our team deployed multilingual AI concierges across web,
          WhatsApp, and Facebook—answering FAQs, handling bookings, and deflecting routine support,
          all while integrating with property systems for accurate, real-time info.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/case-studies/hotel-chatbots" class="text-[#93C5FD] text-xl leading-7">Learn more</a>
          <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- NEW: Media Monitoring & Sentiment (Amharic + English) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 px-2 md:px-6 py-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/0">
        <p class="text-lg font-normal">
          For a media group, we engineered a social listening and monitoring system that tracks
          coverage in Amharic and English, surfaces sentiment trends, and identifies optimal posting
          windows—informing content and ad spend with data-driven insights.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/case-studies/media-monitoring" class="text-[#93C5FD] text-xl leading-7">Learn more</a>
          <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Optional: Education AI Pipelines -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 px-2 md:px-6 py-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/0">
        <p class="text-lg font-normal">
          For an EdTech initiative, we built AI pipelines for story and assignment generation, added
          grammar validation, and ensured alignment to curriculum via retrieval-augmented generation
          and quality checks—delivering consistent, safe content at scale.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/case-studies/edtech-ai" class="text-[#93C5FD] text-xl leading-7">Learn more</a>
          <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Container>
